---
title: Mumbai Chicken & Roast Root Veggies with Mixed Salad & Yoghurt
description: There’s something special about a root vegetable, we can’t get enough of them. Therefore this dish is chocked full of
those yummy colourful veggies. Mumbai-spiced chicken is cooked to juicy tender perfection and add another splash of colour with an apple mixed salad.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mumbai-chicken-roast-potatoes-9fd1e75d.jpg
